<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The addPages() method of Zend_Navigation_Container only takes an array or a Zend_Config instance. It should also accept a Zend_Navigation_Container.</p>

<p>It's a fairly minor fix. Insert the following into the addPages method:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if ($pages instanceof Zend_Navigation_Container) {
    $pages = iterator_to_array($pages);
}
</code></pre>

<p>The docblocks and exception message will also need updating. Note: this uses iterator_to_array instead of getPages so that the order of pages will be consistent with calling toArray().</p>

